Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode.4 title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.91,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 憶 之 笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拉緊鋼索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 那邊太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要隨便放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 放那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 貨物都在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 移動到那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都叫你別用飛的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要切斷鋼索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你能自己想點辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何處理你的居住權 我們尚無定論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能暫時在這裡生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 就 行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Chamber 附近 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賬 單？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求貴官通過勞動補償對機庫造成的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們趕走海賊的可是雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞機庫和那是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雷德剛剛來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們為他免除了逗留期間所消耗的水電費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及將這龐然大物放在船上的裝載費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是只有單方受益的霸王交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我具體內容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這台人形機器人太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 去搬下一箱貨物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到剛剛那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 移動到那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不要飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這人形機器人不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙聽得懂你之外的人說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的話他也會聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據軍紀 在允許範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可移交命令權
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在幹活在幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓破廢鐵幹活 自己卻在一邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大蠢材 果然還是應該把他丟進海裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可能只是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法從貴官的行動中發現意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是集中精神的一種手段罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這麼熱的天 虧他們還能這麼好動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有紀律 他們的教官在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測 兒童的訓練沒有教官參與
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要如何將他們培養成社會的一員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下達下一個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好詐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛到天上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務執行出現障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請批准排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要對他們造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 狀態怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命 中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？你在做什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道還做啊 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯 指甲 這顆星球 上 沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的 話 就 送給 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們邊走邊聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有好禮物可以送給弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟 弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手很巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何謂「弟弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「弟弟」…就是兄弟的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己小的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊社會中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於雌雄配偶及血緣關係而構成的社會單位的名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有過這樣的習俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德沒有家人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低 效率 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低效率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得雷德住的地方很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾好像想問你關於宇宙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙 的 事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他對天體啦 還有能飛向宇宙的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他身體很虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身 體 虛弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的胸部有點疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀河同盟中 體弱的人類將會被淘汰及處分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法參加戰鬥的人是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用…怎麼能這樣 雷德你無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不 懂 你 的提 問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:08:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能從與那個人的對話中得到有意義的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 就去見見奧爾德姆醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾 德姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個醫生 不過大家都稱他為賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是加爾剛蒂亞裡知識最淵博的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 艾米來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我帶了客人來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道就是雷德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說有事想問問醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我還有工作沒有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 一會兒我會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面等著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是聽到過傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是能理解語言的機械所發出的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項技術已經失傳了 沒想到能親眼看到實物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以 提問 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能回答得上 你就儘管問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請教如何才能回到銀河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 以我的知識無法回答你的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 大部分古老的智慧都已失傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是行星穿梭技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們目前所保留的關於天空的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它應該不是你所要找尋的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 幫不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 也沒 辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以再 問 一個 問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽你對這個艦團組織的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂見解是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦團非常沒有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令體系以及軍事訓練也不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的行動也毫無秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解保護弱者的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星來客是這樣看的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所指的效率似乎相當狹義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不妨去見見貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能從與那個人的對話中得到有意義的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有意義應該由你自己判斷
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 醫生也不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}歡迎回來 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是雷德哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是姐姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次 見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是艾米的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話 請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也說想見見貝貝爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這就是Chamber的通信機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的會說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Chamber先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機是用於支援駕駛員的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷 地球的語言也能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人手不夠了 你快來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 帥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得現在氣氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼氣氛正好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是你想的那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 貝貝爾 雷德就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太急了 小心摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 姐姐總是匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥 你真的是從宇宙來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的生活是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河同盟的主要任務是與希迪亞斯進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅人類生存的異種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從銀河同盟創立至今 戰鬥從未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這裡的生活完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪消耗者唯有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 真的很艱辛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你習慣這裡的生活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法理解加爾剛蒂亞的組織構造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請解釋低效及無意義經營的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團不是組織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家聚在一起罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時而吵架 時而互幫互助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這樣的方式活下去罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問意義何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能安心地活著不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此回答感到不解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的行動目的應該是討伐敵人希迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則人類無法獲得穩定的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀河同盟中 你這樣的人類會立刻被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果將希迪亞斯全部都消滅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河同盟會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥你會怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一道命令之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如果沒有下一道命令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繼續待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我們一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為待命不就是指一直活下去的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你的人形機器人被喬給搶走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得當了次英雄 現在卻不成樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道自己的行動是否有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是幫我們趕走海賊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我只是在監視Chamber而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是還沒適應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法判斷我應該採取什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該採取的行動啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放棄你那軍人思維怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 棄？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 更加自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集雨水！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是氣象現象 沒有毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急事態了 用你的人形機器人來收集雨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡水可是很珍貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有帆布 把它展開來收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴官的腦波產生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在意友軍的戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前狀況下 貴官的思考毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總覺得他好可憐…一個人流落到陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帥哥沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你很擔心他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你濕透了呢 會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家把身體擦乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的驟雨很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次觀測到集中降雨現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中也會下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的病人也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我並不認為自己是不被需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 還有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 米？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥也是一直被別人所需要才能活到現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有對戰鬥有益的人才需要存活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 反向思考一下 對雷德哥哥來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有你覺得需要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐 彼此都需要對方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 我需要我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對同盟而言 無意義者沒有生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這對你來說是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽姐姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這是什麼 卻在製作著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是笛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中完全不需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛 子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它可以發出聲音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說錯什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是 我也不 知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是想起什麼悲傷的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你 把它 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是紗雅推薦的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 還是無法定位坐標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測情報不足 仍需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還需要進一步瞭解這個星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要 貴官早晚將與主力部隊會合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道的

